items.preText: baber: "very smart by sarfaraz and pakistan by sending out shadab who is eating deliveries and will put pressure on the rest. equally smart by imam for taking a single off the first ball of the over and giving the strike to shadab."
items.text: full on off, and he drives with the angled bat off the front foot. But stopped by the back off-side field
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Shadab Khan, no run

items.text: full on off, and spinning into Shadab. Defended with soft hands to cover as the infielders come charging in to stop the single
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Shadab Khan, no run

items.text: flighted on middle stump, and the straight drive is drilled to long off for a single. Shadab keeps the strike again
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Shadab Khan, 1 run

items.text: back of a length on middle stump, and the pull has taken a top-edge through to Liton Das! Shadab's frustrating knock comes to an end. His maiden ODI wicket
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Shadab Khan, OUT

dismissal.text: Shadab Khan c Liton Das b Soumya Sarkar 4 (24b 0x4 0x6) SR: 16.66

items.text: good length just outside off stump. He defends with the bat's open face to cover point
items.postText: Osama: "What was the point of sending shadab out cheaply and consumed many deliveries. Poor management!!"
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, no run

items.text: full just outside off, and angling into the batsman. Fended
items.postText: Chowdhury Sayee: "Bad move by Soumya, keeping Shadab was better "
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, no run

items.text: good length outside off, and he carves a cut with the bat's open face to third man. Gets off the mark
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, 1 run

items.text: full just outside off, and he waits for the slower ball to get to him. Opens his bat's face and runs this down to third man
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Imam-ul-Haq, 1 run

items.text: good length, but tight on the fourth-stump line. Punched off the back foot to cover point
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, no run

items.text: full on off stump, and pushed off the front foot to mid on. Well stopped by Soumya, whose been electric on the field today
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Imam-ul-Haq, no run
Mahmudullah to Imam-ul-Haq, no run

items.text: full on off stump, and the ball turns away after pitching. Fended off the front foot
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Imam-ul-Haq, no run

items.text: good length outside off, and angling into the batsman. Too close to his body for the cut, and he misses the shot. But Liton misses too, and that allows Imam to scamper across for byes
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Imam-ul-Haq, 1 bye

items.text: good length just outside off stump, and he turns this off his hips to deep midwicket for a walking single
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Asif Ali, 1 run

items.text: full just outside off, and pushed to cover point for a quick single. Mehidy has a shy at the stumps, but misses
items.postText: Mohammad Isam: Mashrafe has now played against both Inzamam and Imam. He dismissed Inzy in 2003.
items.shortText: Mahmudullah to Imam-ul-Haq, no run

items.text: full on off stump, and whipped off his pads to midwicket
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, no run

items.text: full just outside off. Asif walks down the wicket, and drives with the straight bat to mid off
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, no run

items.text: back of a length outside off stump, and he swivels to pull right over midwicket! Lands just short of the boundary
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, FOUR runs

items.text: good length on off, and angling inwards. Misses the leg-side flick as the ball hits his groin region. Ouch!
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, no run

items.text: good length on middle stump, and clipped off his hips to midwicket for a single
items.shortText: Soumya Sarkar to Asif Ali, 1 run

items.text: low full toss on middle and leg, as Imam tries to muscle a drive. Mistimes it to mid off
